00:06:04.540 --> 00:06:11.440
we label states by 0, 1, 2, 3.

00:06:11.440 --> 00:06:16.150
And that's the eigenvalue
of the number operator

00:06:16.150 --> 00:06:17.810
in the harmonic oscillator.

00:06:17.810 --> 00:06:22.720
So the ground state energy
would correspond to 0,

00:06:22.720 --> 00:06:25.000
has a first order
correction that

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:30.030
would be given by the
unperturbed ground state

00:06:30.030 --> 00:06:36.660
and delta H 0.

