00:06:54.330 --> 00:06:55.350
Easy enough.

00:06:55.350 --> 00:06:57.750
That's what we have to do.

00:06:57.750 --> 00:07:01.410
Now, the evaluation
of that matrix element

00:07:01.410 --> 00:07:04.770
